\Abstract{
The \proglang{R} package \pkg{equate} \citep{albano2016equate} contains functions for observed-score linking and equating under single-group, equivalent-groups, and nonequivalent-groups with anchor test and covariate designs. This paper introduces these designs and provides an overview of observed-score equating with details about each of the supported methods. Examples demonstrate the basic functionality of the \pkg{equate} package.
}
